我怎麼會黏過來的?
What do I do?

351
00:33:04,210 --> 00:33:05,670
別碰我的鬍子?
I said not to pull my beard!

352
00:33:05,740 --> 00:33:06,500
那現在怎麼辦?
Now what?

353
00:33:06,570 --> 00:33:09,540
不要動
D-o-n"-t touch!!

354
00:33:14,320 --> 00:33:15,180
小子
Hey,kid.

355
00:33:15,320 --> 00:33:16,080
你叫我?
Are you calling me?

356
00:33:16,220 --> 00:33:18,280
難道是叫我自己,撿兩塊石頭 是
Of course.Pick two rocks.

357
00:33:19,950 --> 00:33:21,110
大塊點
Bigger ones!

358
00:33:23,460 --> 00:33:24,820
跟我來
Follow me.

359
00:33:28,460 --> 00:33:31,020
我叫你扔就扔,我沒叫你扔,你千萬別扔
Throw only when I tell you.

360
00:33:49,320 --> 00:33:53,080
你們這些所謂正道人士,根基未深
You so-called righteous ones are vulnerable and weak.

361
00:33:53,420 --> 00:33:55,790
所以讓我血魔趁虛而入
You"ve left an opening for me,the Blood Demon.

362
00:33:55,990 --> 00:33:58,650
這個和尚中了我血魔的毒
This Monk has been poisoned by my venom.

363
00:33:58,860 --> 00:34:03,320
在十天之內,他就會毒血攻心走火入魔
Within ten days,the venom will travel to his heart.

364
00:34:03,930 --> 00:34:07,090
那到個時候他就會成為我血魔的替身
And then he"ll become the Blood Demon"s double.

365
00:34:07,530 --> 00:34:10,990
這就叫做道高一尺,魔高一丈
Just remember.Evil is deadlier than righteous.

366
00:34:45,540 --> 00:34:46,600
那是什麼玩意?
What is that?

367
00:34:46,810 --> 00:34:48,170
血魔元神出竅
His soul"s exodus.

368
00:34:48,510 --> 00:34:49,870
元神出竅是什麼?
Exodus?What do you mean?

369
00:35:00,150 --> 00:35:01,710
血魔形體雖然打散了
Even though I have destroyed his body.

370
00:35:01,890 --> 00:35:02,950
元神未滅
His soul still lives.

371
00:35:03,090 --> 00:35:04,850
拿童子骨來保護自己
He uses virgin skulls to protect himself

372
00:35:05,030 --> 00:35:07,290
過些日子,找機會復活
and waits for the chance to resurrect.

373
00:35:13,070 --> 00:35:14,330
捉住我的腳
Grab my feet!

374
00:35:41,460 --> 00:35:44,120
我的浩天鏡也無法徹底除掉他
Even my Sky Mirror cannot destroy his soul.

375
00:35:44,260 --> 00:35:45,630
這次可背鍋了
We"re in trouble this time.

376
00:35:45,870 --> 00:35:47,530
鍋?誰背鍋了?
Who can control him then?

377
00:35:47,930 --> 00:35:52,200
暫時還是我背,我的浩天鏡還可以鎮壓他
For now,my Sky Mirror can subdue him.

378
00:35:52,470 --> 00:35:54,130
不過七七四十九天之後
But when the Big Dipper

379
00:35:54,270 --> 00:35:56,140
天上北斗七星移位
begins to shift in 49 days,

380
00:35:56,840 --> 00:36:01,110
到時候我浩天鏡就會十年一次黯然無光
my Sky Mirror will lose its shine

381
00:36:01,280 --> 00:36:02,540
威力全無
and will be rendered powerless.

382
00:36:02,750 --> 00:36:03,610
那怎麼辦?
What will happen then?

383
00:36:03,850 --> 00:36:05,820
那時候由你背了
Then it"ll be up to you.

384
00:36:05,950 --> 00:36:07,110
我來背?
Me?

385
00:36:07,250 --> 00:36:09,420
不是你背,難道還是我背?
Yes!Who else?

386
00:36:09,660 --> 00:36:12,820
你有聽說過沒有,長江後浪推前浪
Lt"s time for the next generation to take over.

387
00:36:12,990 --> 00:36:14,550
峨嵋開山有兩把劍
Ou-Mei had two exceptional swords,

388
00:36:14,730 --> 00:36:16,700
一把紫郢劍,一把青索劍
Purple and Green,

389
00:36:16,900 --> 00:36:18,160
人稱紫青雙劍
known as the Twin Swords.

390
00:36:18,370 --> 00:36:20,130
十八年前女神李亦奇
18 years ago Girl Wonder,Li l-Chi,

391
00:36:20,330 --> 00:36:23,390
帶了這兩把劍去天外天洞內洞苦修
took them to Cave Beyond to study.

392
00:36:23,540 --> 00:36:26,600
現在只要拿到這兩把劍就可消滅這元神
Only these two swords can destroy the Blood Demon"s soul.

393
00:36:26,770 --> 00:36:27,930
那天外天洞內洞怎麼去?
How do you get to Cave Beyond?

394
00:36:28,170 --> 00:36:30,540
天外天洞內洞的入口在天刀峰
It is on Heaven"s Blade Peak.

395
00:36:30,680 --> 00:36:32,140
現在你即刻起程
You must go now.

396
00:36:32,350 --> 00:36:34,400
如果遲了被他出了竅
Once the exodus takes place,

397
00:36:34,550 --> 00:36:38,610
到時候集天下三仙二老一子七僧的法力
then nothing in this world will be

398
00:36:38,720 --> 00:36:39,580
也沒有辦法了
able to stop the Blood Demon.

399
00:36:39,820 --> 00:36:40,580
你聽到了沒有?
Did you hear me?

400
00:36:40,790 --> 00:36:41,550
那你呢?
What about you?

401
00:36:41,790 --> 00:36:44,760
你傻的,如果我去了誰來對付他?快去
Don"t be silly.I have to stay to control him.Now go!

402
00:36:47,760 --> 00:36:48,820
還不快去
What are you waiting for?

403
00:36:54,300 --> 00:36:55,060
師父
Teacher!

404
00:36:55,270 --> 00:36:58,030
崑崙第十八代弟子一真,跪下接令
Kun-Lun"s 18th generation disciple,Yi-Chen.Kneel down!

405
00:37:01,410 --> 00:37:05,070
從現在開始你就是崑崙派第十八代掌門人
You are now the 18th Chief of the Kun-Lun Clan!

406
00:37:05,280 --> 00:37:06,340
接令
Take the order.

407
00:37:07,650 --> 00:37:09,910
這一串是崑崙掌門法珠
These are the Chief's beads.

408
00:37:10,050 --> 00:37:12,210
一真,你要記住
Yi Chen!Remember,as Chief,

409
00:37:12,350 --> 00:37:15,010
身為掌門要負起一門的責任
you are responsible for the entire Clan.

410
00:37:15,260 --> 00:37:17,220
要承先繼後耀我崑崙
And for bringing glory to Kun-Lun!

411
00:37:19,460 --> 00:37:21,220
師父,你可別看不開
Teacher,don"t do it!

412
00:37:21,360 --> 00:37:22,520
你不要管我
Don"t mind me!

413
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:27,360
我這樣怎麼做掌門人?
How can I be the Chief like this?

414
00:37:34,240 --> 00:37:35,300
那塊石頭呢?
Where"s the rock?

415
00:37:37,440 --> 00:37:38,710
師父
Teacher!

416
00:37:40,910 --> 00:37:42,470
你認為你封了經脈就可以自殺了嗎?
You think you can just kill yourself?

417
00:37:42,650 --> 00:37:44,010
我要治好你 我不讓你治
I will find someone to cure you!I don"t want you to!

418
00:37:44,220 --> 00:37:45,880
我要治好你 我不讓你治
I want to!I don"t want you to!

419
00:37:46,020 --> 00:37:47,180
不要吵
Shut up!

420
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:54,090
你剛才跟誰說話?
Who were you talking to just now?

421
00:37:56,230 --> 00:37:58,600
我是掌門人,我不准...
I am the Chief,I...

422
00:38:02,240 --> 00:38:05,900
師父,我不是有意的,我把它穿起來好了
l"m sorry,Teacher.I didn"t mean to.L"ll restring it.

423
00:38:06,670 --> 00:38:08,730
想不到這個世界亂成這樣
The world is in more disarray than I thought.

424
00:38:09,640 --> 00:38:12,610
本來我想求你們搭救我們凡夫俗子的
I had originally asked you to save us mortals.

425
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:16,250
現在不知道誰救誰
Now I really can"t tell who is saving who.

426
00:38:16,420 --> 00:38:18,780
今天七七四十九天的第一天
Today is the first day of the 49 days.

427
00:38:19,220 --> 00:38:21,380
讓我帶這個和尚去治好了病
Let me get this Monk cured first.

428
00:38:21,550 --> 00:38:25,220
然後我立刻去找紫青雙劍,希望還來得及
Then l"ll go after the Twin Swords before time runs out.

429
00:38:38,170 --> 00:38:39,230
那是什麼東西?
What is it?

430
00:38:39,440 --> 00:38:40,500
有魚了
Fish.

431
00:38:45,550 --> 00:38:47,210
下面很有勁 是嗎
It"s great down there!Really?

432
00:38:58,960 --> 00:39:00,930
還走...
Still trying to run?

433
00:39:09,540 --> 00:39:11,090
那條魚戲弄我
Darn it.

434
00:39:14,010 --> 00:39:15,370
你這死魚
You bad fish!

435
00:39:24,480 --> 00:39:25,540
電鰻
Lt"s charged!

436
00:39:30,460 --> 00:39:32,220
小卒子,它還很有氣
Soldier,l"ve got the fish here!

437
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:57,750
小和尚
Little Monk.

438
00:39:58,950 --> 00:39:59,710
什麼事?
What?

439
00:39:59,950 --> 00:40:05,020
吃過沒有?我以前也做過幾天和尚的
Have you ever had fish?I was once a monk for a few days.

440
00:40:05,230 --> 00:40:10,600
那大師說吃熟的魚就不算殺生的,試試吧
I was told that eating cooked fish is not considered killing.Want some?

441
00:40:16,700 --> 00:40:17,970
真的不算殺生?
Are you sure?

442
00:40:18,100 --> 00:40:19,260
不算
Positive!

443
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:23,440
師伯
Master Ting.

444
00:40:31,950 --> 00:40:34,510
這不是師父,這是血魔的替身
That"s not Master Ting!That"s the Blood Demon"s double!

445
00:40:34,690 --> 00:40:35,850
那把劍呢?
Where"s that sword?

446
00:40:36,060 --> 00:40:36,920
在你後面
Right behind you!

447
00:40:44,560 --> 00:40:46,120
那個是真的那個是假的?
Which one is real and which is the double?

448
00:41:04,580 --> 00:41:06,250
怎麼變成女的了?
He"s turned into a woman!

449
00:41:12,490 --> 00:41:13,360
回鞘
Sheathe!

450
00:41:17,660 --> 00:41:19,720
邪魔妖孽無孔不入,你們要小心知道嗎?
Evil is omnipresent.Be careful!

451
00:41:19,930 --> 00:41:20,700
知道
Yes.

452
00:41:22,140 --> 00:41:23,300
一真,什麼東西?
What is that?

453
00:41:25,540 --> 00:41:27,700
是魚,我剛剛抓住
Lt"s a fish.

454
00:41:28,070 --> 00:41:29,630
想把它放生,積點陰德
I was just about to free it.Have mercy on all living things!

455
00:41:35,750 --> 00:41:37,510
如果沒事,我們去瑤池仙堡
We"d better get going to the Fort.

456
00:41:39,120 --> 00:41:43,990
幸虧師伯不知道魚是熟的,還給你
Good thing he didn"t know the fish was cooked!Take it back.

457
00:41:55,170 --> 00:41:56,430
幾位可以請回
You may all leave.

458
00:41:57,170 --> 00:42:00,540
這位大師中的毒我無法醫治
I cannot cure this Monk.

459
00:42:03,140 --> 00:42:04,910
望聞問切,是斷症四大基要
You didn"t even diagnose him.

460
00:42:05,110 --> 00:42:06,980
你不聞不問,怎麼知道無法醫治呢?
How do you know you cannot cure him?

461
00:42:07,210 --> 00:42:08,580
你錯了,除非是我們堡主出關
Only the Countess can cure him.

462
00:42:08,750 --> 00:42:09,610
堡主?
Countess?

463
00:42:09,820 --> 00:42:11,480
原來你們還有一位堡主
We didn"t know you have a Countess.

464
00:42:11,620 --> 00:42:13,090
我們堡主閉關多年
The Countess has been in seclusion for years.

465
00:42:14,250 --> 00:42:16,120
你們想她出關,除非...
She"ll not come out and cure him,unless...

466
00:42:16,320 --> 00:42:17,380
除非什麼?
Unless what?

467
00:42:19,030 --> 00:42:20,190
除非是有緣人
Unless he is sent by Fate.

468
00:42:25,500 --> 00:42:27,860
仙堡冰焰每天燃燒一次
Our Fort Flame burns once everyday,

469
00:42:28,000 --> 00:42:31,460
燃燒的時間有時長有時短
sometimes long,sometimes short.

470
00:42:31,840 --> 00:42:33,400
在冰焰熄滅之前
During this period of time,

471
00:42:33,640 --> 00:42:35,300
凡病人見到堡主
if she comes out,

472
00:42:35,640 --> 00:42:38,510
堡主必定悉力以赴治好他
the Countess will heal anyone who comes for help.

473
00:42:39,950 --> 00:42:43,710
現在冰焰將盡,我們的堡主還沒出現
The Flame is about to burn out and the Countess has not shown yet.

474
00:42:44,780 --> 00:42:47,750
看來各位並非是有緣之人
Looks like it is fate that the Monk does not get treated.

475
00:42:48,220 --> 00:42:50,690
那...我師父怎麼辦?
Then what happens to my Teacher?

476
00:42:52,060 --> 00:42:54,030
國有國法,家有家規
The Fort has its rules.

477
00:42:54,190 --> 00:42:57,560
既然我們身在仙堡,就要尊重仙堡的規矩
Now that we"re here,we must abide by its rules.

478
00:43:04,300 --> 00:43:06,770
我丁引以一身元氣,務令冰焰長燃
I,Ting-Yin,will sustain the flame

479
00:43:07,370 --> 00:43:11,040
縱使全身化為烏有,我丁引也在所不惜
even if it takes all the forces out of my body!

480
00:43:11,540 --> 00:43:12,910
我們有言在先
I thought we had agreed

481
00:43:13,010 --> 00:43:15,570
一切的事聽命天地間一個緣字
to trust everything to fate!

482
00:43:15,950 --> 00:43:19,110
是,我現在要做的就是阻止你的制做孽緣
Yes,that"s why l"m trying to stop you from creating ill fate!

483
00:43:43,140 --> 00:43:44,510
不是那個妖女嗎?
Hey,there"s that witch!

484
00:43:45,450 --> 00:43:46,310
我們中計了
We"ve been trapped!

485
00:44:25,120 --> 00:44:27,590
小卒子...
Soldier...Soldier...Soldier!

486
00:44:29,190 --> 00:44:30,050
師伯
Master Ting.

487
00:44:31,060 --> 00:44:32,820
你不能見了女人都叫妖女
Don"tjust call every woman you see a witch!

488
00:44:33,530 --> 00:44:34,990
師伯,不是
No,Master Ting.

489
00:44:35,160 --> 00:44:35,920
不是什麼?
What do you mean "no"?

490
00:44:36,060 --> 00:44:38,220
那個堡主明明是妖女的樣子
She really looked like the witch we saw!

491
00:44:38,360 --> 00:44:39,230
你才是妖女
You are witch.

492
00:44:39,470 --> 00:44:42,630
聽泉台的妖道用移形遁光法騙你們
That was evil disguised as the Countess.

493
00:44:42,800 --> 00:44:43,770
你們上當了
You"ve been fooled.

494
00:44:46,140 --> 00:44:47,610
你要打醒十二精神
Now you stand guard.

495
00:44:47,810 --> 00:44:49,670
現在我要給他開任督二脈
I have to bring his veins into unison.

496
00:44:49,880 --> 00:44:53,330
打通任督二脈,那不是傳授武功給他
Bring his veins into unison?That"s like teaching him how to fight!

497
00:44:53,580 --> 00:44:54,840
他應該謝謝你才對
He has you to thank for that.

498
00:45:59,680 --> 00:46:02,340
師父...
Teacher...Teacher.

499
00:46:07,190 --> 00:46:08,240
大俠
Master Ting.

500
00:46:08,620 --> 00:46:11,390
不要出聲,現在我跟你一氣相連
Not a sound!L"m transfusing energy into you.

501
00:46:11,690 --> 00:46:15,150
稍有不慎,你我兩個人經脈都會盡毀
Any mishap,both our veins will be shot and we"ll die.

502
00:46:16,460 --> 00:46:17,720
那我怎麼辦?
What should I do?

503
00:46:18,230 --> 00:46:20,290
普神合一,意如流水
Concentrate and let your will guide you.

504
00:46:47,160 --> 00:46:49,020
這麼踩師父怎麼修道嗎?
That"s no way to treat a monk!

505
00:46:59,710 --> 00:47:01,070
我這麼厲害
L"ve turned into a super man!

506
00:47:17,290 --> 00:47:19,450
你這麼做,是什麼意思嗎?
Why are you doing this?

507
00:47:19,630 --> 00:47:21,490
難道你不想治好這個和尚嗎?
Don"t you want to save this monk?

508
00:48:10,640 --> 00:48:12,800
冷不冷嗎?很冷
Are you cold?Very.

509
00:48:12,980 --> 00:48:16,640
那班丫鬟站在門口,我們怎樣到裡面去看
How can we get passed these girls to get inside?

510
00:48:17,620 --> 00:48:18,880
你們看什麼?
Hey!What are you staring at?

511
00:48:26,690 --> 00:48:29,860
這麼凶,很難說服她們讓我們進去了
What a temper!It doesn"t look like they"ll let us through.

512
00:48:31,430 --> 00:48:32,800
不知道有沒有別的進口
I wonder if there is another entrance.

513
00:48:35,400 --> 00:48:38,170
這兒這麼大當然有,我們找找看
L"m sure there is one in here!Let"s look for it!

514
00:48:43,140 --> 00:48:44,300
你們想幹什麼?
Hey!What are you doing?

515
00:48:44,440 --> 00:48:47,410
沒什麼,小妹妹,我們想找個地方解個手
Nothing.We just need to use the toilet,sister.

516
00:48:48,080 --> 00:48:49,240
行不行嗎?不行
Can we?You can"t!

517
00:48:50,320 --> 00:48:52,780
仙堡之內外人不可以亂闖亂撞
Strangers may not wander around in the Fort!

518
00:48:53,520 --> 00:48:55,990
沒關係,急起來到處都是茅房
That"s all right.We"ll just do it right here.

519
00:48:56,220 --> 00:48:56,980
你敢?
Don"t you dare!

520
00:48:57,220 --> 00:48:58,190
不敢
No?

521
00:49:02,530 --> 00:49:03,890
你儘管試試
I dare you!

522
00:49:04,330 --> 00:49:06,390
試一試?試就試,怕什麼?
All right.You said it!

523
00:49:11,700 --> 00:49:13,370
你以為這樣就可以嚇唬我了嗎?
You think that will scare me?

524
00:49:19,110 --> 00:49:20,370
幹麼你這麼狠?
You are too much!

525
00:49:20,550 --> 00:49:21,710
千萬別告訴我師父
Better not tell my Teacher!

526
00:49:52,950 --> 00:49:53,710
曉如
Hsiao-Yu!

527
00:49:53,810 --> 00:49:56,680
堡主閉關三年,一出關就消耗很多真氣
The healing has exhausted

528
00:49:56,920 --> 00:49:58,180
所以需要休息
the Countess and she needs her rest.

529
00:49:58,320 --> 00:49:59,980
現在和尚的毒已經解了
The monk"s venom has been dissolved.

530
00:50:00,150 --> 00:50:03,210
請你們別再打擾堡主,請
The two of you should leave the Fort.Please.

531
00:50:17,070 --> 00:50:18,540
小卒子,這兒有個洞
Soldier,there"s a hole ahead.

532
00:50:20,210 --> 00:50:21,260
有洞就鑽好了
Just get in.

533
00:50:24,480 --> 00:50:25,640
這是什麼洞?
What kind of hole is this?

534
00:50:26,880 --> 00:50:28,040
救命...
Help!

535
00:50:28,810 --> 00:50:32,080
小卒子,快救我
Help!

536
00:50:42,390 --> 00:50:45,160
你醒醒...你沒死吧?
Wake up!Are you dead?

537
00:50:45,900 --> 00:50:46,760
我在什麼地方?
Where am I?

538
00:50:46,970 --> 00:50:47,730
你怎麼不會游水?
Can"t you swim?

539
00:50:47,900 --> 00:50:48,870
我不會游水的
No,I can"t swim.

540
00:50:55,510 --> 00:50:56,770
飛劍
Flying swords!!

541
00:51:00,810 --> 00:51:03,680
你們這些臭八婆,這麼喜歡看就看吧
You bitches!See all you want then!

542
00:51:14,060 --> 00:51:15,220
連那條都沒有了
There goes that one too!

543
00:51:26,740 --> 00:51:29,000
我要帶你們兩個人去見你們的師父
L"m going to take you to your teachers.

544
00:51:29,210 --> 00:51:31,370
讓他們知道你們怎麼傷風敗俗
To show them how you"re giving your Clan a bad name!

545
00:51:32,080 --> 00:51:34,440
不要...大姐我求求你別告訴我師父
I beg you.Please don"t tell my Teacher.

546
00:51:34,650 --> 00:51:37,010
勝敗乃兵家常事,怕什麼?見就見
You win some,you lose some.There"s nothing to be afraid of!

547
00:51:37,720 --> 00:51:39,380
讓我師父知道我拉她褲腰帶
If Teacher finds out I pulled at her pants,

548
00:51:39,520 --> 00:51:41,180
我真變成傷風敗俗了
I will be in big trouble!

549
00:51:41,750 --> 00:51:43,120
拉褲腰帶有什麼關係
Pulling her pants is no big deal!

550
00:51:43,420 --> 00:51:44,480
什麼?
What?

551
00:51:44,620 --> 00:51:45,490
怎麼?
What now?

552
00:51:45,660 --> 00:51:46,630
你別再讓她生氣了
Please don"t be mad.

553
00:51:46,790 --> 00:51:48,450
大姐,你叫我做什麼我就做什麼
L"ll do whatever it takes to make it up to you.

554
00:51:48,630 --> 00:51:51,890
大事化小事,小事化無事,只要沒事就行
Just don"t make this any bigger than it is.

555
00:51:52,530 --> 00:51:55,800
這樣,好,你打他,他打你
Fine.Then slap each other until

556
00:51:55,970 --> 00:51:57,830
打到我的氣順了為止
my nerves are calmed.

557
00:51:59,040 --> 00:52:01,510
你氣順了我的氣可不順
Then my nerves will not be calm!

558
00:52:01,670 --> 00:52:05,540
你們有沒有說過士可殺不可辱,我不打
Haven"t you heard that a man would rather be killed than insulted?

559
00:52:05,740 --> 00:52:08,910
還這麼嘴硬,見你們師父去
Then l"ll bring you to see your teachers.

560
00:52:09,750 --> 00:52:12,010
他們又不是我師父,見就見
Fine with me.They"re not my teachers anyway.

561
00:52:13,220 --> 00:52:17,180
不行...小卒子,你打我好了,打我
No,no!Soldier,why don"t you just slap me?

562
00:52:17,320 --> 00:52:18,090
我不打兄弟的
I don"t hit my buddies.

563
00:52:18,290 --> 00:52:20,350
你別把我當你的兄弟,打我好了,打我
Don"t consider me your buddy.Just do it.

564
00:52:20,530 --> 00:52:21,990
我不打...
I won"t do it.

565
00:52:23,460 --> 00:52:25,230
那我自己打我自己
Then l"ll slap myself.

566
00:52:30,100 --> 00:52:32,470
你這麼沒骨氣,怎麼做掌門?
Have a little backbone!How can you be Chief of a Clan?

567
00:52:34,410 --> 00:52:36,170
我看也做不了
I was planning to give that up anyway.

568
00:52:48,990 --> 00:52:50,250
我頂
Block!

569
00:52:52,360 --> 00:52:55,420
幸虧我法寶沒出齊,否則以為我沒玩意
Good thing I still have a few tricks up my sleeves.

570
00:53:14,750 --> 00:53:17,510
既然冰焰已盡,就是說緣於此
The Flame died.It is fate that we should part.

571
00:53:18,680 --> 00:53:20,950
堡主,我們後會有期
Until we meet again,Countess.

572
00:53:30,530 --> 00:53:33,500
既然緣盡於此,怎麼會後會有期?
If it is fate that we should part,why should we meet again?

573
00:53:34,800 --> 00:53:37,670
冰緣盡情緣了,為什麼還肯出來見我?
If it is fate that we should part,then why did you come out to see me?

574
00:53:37,900 --> 00:53:39,560
我出來不是為了見你
I didn"t come out to see you.

575
00:53:39,710 --> 00:53:42,070
不是為了見我,難道為了打我?
No?Did you come out to fight me then?

576
00:53:42,240 --> 00:53:44,000
姓丁的你說得對
Ting-Yin,you are right.

577
00:53:44,180 --> 00:53:47,540
當日醫病你對我無禮 ,我要一雪當日之恥
You must pay for the other day when you took advantage of me.

578
00:53:48,540 --> 00:53:51,910
無禮 ?你不是消耗過度,神智不清嗎?
Took advantage?Have you lost your mind from over exhaustion?

579
00:53:52,110 --> 00:53:56,270
當日你突然暈倒,我順手相扶這算無禮 ?
The other day you fainted,and I tried to help you!

580
00:53:56,450 --> 00:53:58,420
我丁某只知道非禮 ,你教教我吧
You tell me if that was taking advantage of you.

581
00:53:59,050 --> 00:53:59,910
我...
I...

582
00:54:00,190 --> 00:54:01,550
你...你說
You tell me!

583
00:54:01,820 --> 00:54:04,580
姓丁的,你太狂妄了,我要教訓你
Ting,you"re too arrogant.I must teach you a lesson.

584
00:54:13,330 --> 00:54:15,490
就用兩招來教訓我,太少了吧
Just two moves?That doesn"t make for much of a lesson!

585
00:54:51,900 --> 00:54:53,770
我知道你有事在身,我放你一馬
I know you have important business to tend to.L"ll let you go.

586
00:54:53,940 --> 00:54:55,100
是嗎?
Really?

587
00:54:55,440 --> 00:54:57,410
我留下三招,等你回來再打
L"ll save three moves for your return.

588
00:54:58,540 --> 00:55:00,100
你有膽等我就有膽回來
If you can wait,I will return.

589
00:55:00,450 --> 00:55:01,910
好,我們擊掌為約
Good.Let"s make a pledge!

590
00:55:16,130 --> 00:55:18,490
一真...
Yi-Chen...Yi-Chen...

591
00:55:24,540 --> 00:55:27,300
這樣也好,你就留下照顧你師父吧
That"s fine.You will stay to take care of your teacher then.

592
00:55:34,680 --> 00:55:35,840
你可以出來了
You can come out now.

593
00:55:38,280 --> 00:55:40,050
我早知道你一定跟著我來的
I knew you"d follow me.

594
00:55:40,890 --> 00:55:43,350
你手無寸鐵,發生了事怎麼辦?
You"re not even armed.What do you do if something happens?

595
00:55:44,720 --> 00:55:47,190
你有兩把劍,給我一把防身吧
You have two swords.You can give me one!

596
00:55:51,560 --> 00:55:54,530
這把劍我是留著送給我徒弟的
L"ve been saving this sword for my student.

597
00:55:55,830 --> 00:55:56,890
師父
Teacher!

598
00:55:57,240 --> 00:55:59,900
你不要表錯情,我還沒想收徒弟
Don"t misunderstand me.L"m not taking students yet.

599
00:56:00,640 --> 00:56:03,200
這把劍我暫時借給你用好了
But I can let you borrow this sword for now.

600
00:56:06,810 --> 00:56:07,970
拿去吧
Take it.

601
00:56:10,050 --> 00:56:11,810
也好,總比沒有好
I guess it"s better than nothing.

602
00:56:23,430 --> 00:56:24,400
大俠
Master Ting!

603
00:56:33,610 --> 00:56:35,160
糟了,有人出事了
Oh no,someone is in trouble!

604
00:56:36,470 --> 00:56:37,940
大俠...
Master Ting,Master Ting!

605
00:56:44,520 --> 00:56:46,180
我的臉色是不是很難看
Does my face look terrible?

606
00:56:47,290 --> 00:56:50,050
不是,不是算十分難看
No,not too bad.

607
00:56:52,190 --> 00:56:54,450
我已經封了自己的九大經脈
L"ve tried to slow the poison from spreading,

608
00:56:54,760 --> 00:56:56,730
紙是包不住火的
but I can"t control it much longer.

609
