不怕,我馬上送你去仙堡
Let"s get you back to the Fort right away.

610
00:57:01,770 --> 00:57:04,630
狄明奇,你是不是很想做我徒弟?
Ti Ming-Chi,are you still anxious/to be my student?

611
00:57:06,740 --> 00:57:08,800
叩三個頭你就是我的收弟
Bow to me three times and you"ll be my student.

612
00:57:09,040 --> 00:57:11,100
這把劍永遠屬於你
This sword will belong to you forever!

613
