師父的話你聽不聽?聽
Do you obey your teacher"s orders?Yes.

614
00:57:24,890 --> 00:57:26,450
我要你答應我一件事
I want you to promise me one thing.

615
00:57:27,190 --> 00:57:30,960
如果三天之內到不了仙堡,你就要殺了我
If we don"t make it to the Fort within three days,kill me.

616
00:57:32,160 --> 00:57:38,630
聽見了沒有,殺了我,殺...
Did you hear me?Kill me!Kill,kill,kill!

617
00:57:42,940 --> 00:57:45,710
殺...
Kill...

618
00:57:50,650 --> 00:57:51,410
他...
He...

619
00:57:52,450 --> 00:57:53,820
怎麼你也中毒
Oh,you got poisoned too?

620
00:57:55,020 --> 00:57:56,680
快點叫堡主出來救他
Hurry!Go ask the Countess to come out and save him!

621
00:57:57,060 --> 00:57:59,420
大師,堡主出不出來救他
Abbot,whether the Countess comes out

622
00:57:59,620 --> 00:58:01,490
要看他跟堡主有沒有緣
will depend on his fate.

623
00:58:01,990 --> 00:58:04,960
冰焰盡,情緣了,是仙堡規矩
She abides by the rule of the Flame.

624
00:58:05,160 --> 00:58:05,930
規矩?
Rule?

625
00:58:06,100 --> 00:58:08,360
是的,師父,救你的時候,就是這樣的
Yes,Teacher.It was the same when we brought you here.

626
00:58:08,570 --> 00:58:11,430
住口,你是崑崙派的叛徒,輪不到你說話
Quiet!You"re a Kun-Lun traitor.It is not your place to talk.

627
00:58:12,540 --> 00:58:13,600
冰焰?
The Flame?

628
00:58:13,770 --> 00:58:14,740
不錯
That"s right.

629
00:58:15,070 --> 00:58:18,340
那麼去點,快...
Then hurry up...hurry...hurry.

630
00:58:27,250 --> 00:58:28,220
堡主
Countess!

631
