身為佛門弟子,竟然這麼毫無修養
How can a monk be so contemptuous?

632
00:58:36,160 --> 00:58:38,720
這兒是瑤池仙堡,你以為是崑崙山麼?
You are at the Fort,not at your own Kun-Lun Mountain!

633
00:58:53,780 --> 00:58:55,540
再不叫堡主出來我就不客氣了
Get the Countess now or you will be sorry!

634
00:58:59,080 --> 00:59:00,640
你不客氣,我也不客氣
Try anything and YOU will be sorry!

635
00:59:01,220 --> 00:59:03,590
你們這些女人,閒來沒事做
You women have nothing else better to do

636
00:59:03,720 --> 00:59:06,590
整天躲在這種地方,想出古靈精怪的規矩
than to hide here and make up these ridiculous rules.

637
00:59:06,820 --> 00:59:09,090
我做和尚也是為了你們這些女人
You were the reason I became a Monk!

638
00:59:09,590 --> 00:59:10,650
我不理你們
L"m wasting my breath!

639
00:59:10,760 --> 00:59:12,320
你有膽子就出來
You!Come out if you have any guts at all!

640
00:59:12,660 --> 00:59:14,130
沒膽子就一輩子躲在裡邊算了
Otherwise stay in there forever,

641
00:59:14,330 --> 00:59:15,390
臭八婆
stupid old maid!

642
00:59:18,370 --> 00:59:21,430
曉如,過門就是客,何必強人所難
Hsiao-Yu!We are guests here.We must not impose.

643
00:59:24,980 --> 00:59:28,940
堡主跟我有言在先,說我一定會回來
I had promised the Countess that I would be back.

644
00:59:30,520 --> 00:59:32,380
想不到竟然一語成
I just didn"t know it would be under these circumstances.

645
00:59:37,560 --> 00:59:38,420
師父
Teacher.

646
00:59:38,620 --> 00:59:39,990
徒弟
Student.

647
00:59:40,120 --> 00:59:41,180
師父
Teacher.

648
00:59:44,630 --> 00:59:46,290
你現在是南海門門人
You are now a Nan-Hai student.

649
00:59:46,460 --> 00:59:48,430
我要你執行南海門門規
You must do your duty according to the Nan-Hai Principles.

650
00:59:48,630 --> 00:59:51,800
為了除魔滅妖,大義滅親
"To destroy evil,even your dearest must not be spared."

651
00:59:53,200 --> 00:59:54,470
快點
Do it now!

652
01:00:02,750 --> 01:00:03,910
快點
Quick!

653
01:00:11,560 --> 01:00:15,320
大義滅親,冰焰盡,情緣了,都是放屁
To hell with fate and rules and principles!

654
01:00:15,660 --> 01:00:18,930
看著活人不醫,看著一點火焰做人
We"re letting a man die because of a flame!

655
01:00:19,100 --> 01:00:21,460
去你的冰焰,去你的規矩
To hell with your flame!

656
01:00:21,670 --> 01:00:24,730
你們都是一盤散沙...我不殺...
You all have lost your minds.I won"t do it!I won"t kill!!

657
01:00:31,180 --> 01:00:34,140
別攔著我...
Get out of my way...

658
01:00:46,760 --> 01:00:48,020
還不放手
Get your hand off of me!

659
01:00:49,360 --> 01:00:50,620
你出來了
Lt"s about time!

660
01:00:51,960 --> 01:00:53,620
姬無霜 堡主
Chi Wu-Shuang.Countess.

661
01:00:53,760 --> 01:00:57,330
竭盡所能,聽天由命,你明白嗎?
We try our best and leave the rest to fate.Do you understand?

662
01:00:57,600 --> 01:00:58,660
堡主,你...
Countess,you...

663
01:00:58,870 --> 01:01:01,630
既然一定要發生的事,就讓他發生吧
Just let what"s meant to happen,happen.

664
01:01:43,710 --> 01:01:44,480
什麼事?
What is wrong?

665
01:01:44,650 --> 01:01:46,210
堡主為了醫你元氣大傷
The Countess already used up her energy when healing you.

666
01:01:46,320 --> 01:01:49,080
現在再醫你的朋友,恐怕對她有危險
Now to heal your friend,she is endangering her own life.

667
01:01:51,720 --> 01:01:55,280
丁引,我醫治你朋友,已經耗盡元氣
Ting-Yin,l"ve used up my energy on your friend.

668
01:01:58,160 --> 01:02:01,530
現在,我不夠真氣再治你了
Now I am too weak to help you.

669
01:02:01,630 --> 01:02:04,500
命在醫者手,既然這樣
If that is the way,then so be it.

670
01:02:05,840 --> 01:02:08,000
堡主,你殺我吧
Countess,please kill me.

671
01:02:10,680 --> 01:02:12,040
我是有這個打算
I do plan to.

672
01:02:12,610 --> 01:02:13,870
我明白
I understand.

673
01:02:32,300 --> 01:02:34,260
含笑身犧牲
"I sacrifice my life with no regrets"

674
01:02:34,530 --> 01:02:37,000
一朝了恩仇
"We will meet again in another world"

675
01:02:57,760 --> 01:03:00,320
堡主給我打傷了,快點去救他
l"ve injured the Countess.Help her,quick!

676
01:03:02,030 --> 01:03:03,580
師父 師伯
Teacher!Master Ting!

677
01:03:03,730 --> 01:03:04,700
你沒事吧
Are you all right?

678
01:03:27,250 --> 01:03:28,510
師父 師伯
Teacher!Master Ting!

679
01:04:40,320 --> 01:04:41,380
丁引
Ting-Yin!

680
01:04:49,800 --> 01:04:51,360
師父...
Teacher!Teacher!

681
01:04:53,400 --> 01:04:55,270
你看看你,把他打成這樣
See,see how badly you"ve beaten him!

682
01:04:55,770 --> 01:04:58,140
好吧,你們這兒誰可以做主
All right,who makes decisions here?

683
