No one?Then l"ll do it.

684
01:05:02,450 --> 01:05:06,510
從現在開始,他有什麼事,由我來負責
From now on,I will be responsible for him.

685
01:05:20,100 --> 01:05:25,560
放開我...
Let go of me!

686
01:05:31,280 --> 01:05:32,040
你幹什麼?
What are you doing?

687
01:05:32,180 --> 01:05:33,440
你真的想打死他
Do you really want to kill him?

688
01:05:33,680 --> 01:05:34,940
我說過他的事由我負責
I said l"m responsible for him.

689
01:05:36,510 --> 01:05:38,380
放開我...
Let me go!Let me go!Let go...

690
01:05:39,250 --> 01:05:40,010
你放開我
Let go of me...

691
01:05:40,280 --> 01:05:42,750
你先下來,讓我來想辦法,快點下來
You get down first.We"ll figure something else.

692
01:05:43,250 --> 01:05:47,820
放開我...
Let go of me!

693
01:05:59,440 --> 01:06:00,500
你是不是想殺他?
Do you really want him dead?

694
01:06:00,600 --> 01:06:01,660
死和尚,走開
Get lost,you stupid Monk!

695
01:06:01,870 --> 01:06:03,130
你要殺他就先殺我
You"ll have to kill me first!

696
01:06:17,720 --> 01:06:18,880
堡主
Countess.

697
01:06:20,060 --> 01:06:23,820
你們快點走,我要打破銅鏡冰封這兒
You must all go now.L"ve to break the Ice Mirror and freeze this place.

698
01:06:23,960 --> 01:06:26,020
堡主,那你自己怎麼出去?
Countess!How will you get out then?

699
01:06:26,160 --> 01:06:27,430
不能讓丁引出去
Don"t let Ting-Yin get out.

700
01:06:27,570 --> 01:06:28,730
不要管我
Don"t worry about me.Just go.

701
01:06:29,330 --> 01:06:30,390
為什麼不殺他
Why didn"t you kill him?

702
01:06:35,610 --> 01:06:36,370
快點離開仙堡
Get out of the Fort now!

703
01:06:36,610 --> 01:06:37,370
快點離開仙堡
Get out of the Fort now!

704
01:06:37,580 --> 01:06:38,840
為什麼?為什麼?
Why?Why?

705
01:06:44,520 --> 01:06:45,570
堡主
Countess!

706
01:06:47,320 --> 01:06:48,180
來不及了
Lt"s too late!

707
01:07:35,370 --> 01:07:37,730
師父...
Teacher...Teacher...

708
01:07:39,740 --> 01:07:40,800
都怪你不好
It"s all your fault.

709
01:07:40,940 --> 01:07:43,410
你不帶你師父來就不會連累我師父
If you hadn"t brought Ting-Yin here,my Teacher would be fine.

710
01:07:44,140 --> 01:07:48,410
快救我師父出來...
You"d better get my Teacher out!You get my Teacher out!

711
01:07:57,690 --> 01:08:00,450
整個仙堡都冰封,你們兩個在這兒幹什麼
The Fort is freezing over.What are you two still doing here?

712
01:08:00,620 --> 01:08:01,490
不要管我
Lt"s none of your business!

713
01:08:02,890 --> 01:08:04,050
有血
There"s blood!

714
01:08:11,400 --> 01:08:12,770
你封不住我的
You can"t keep me here!

715
01:08:18,910 --> 01:08:19,770
什麼事
What"s happening?

716
01:08:19,980 --> 01:08:22,240
冰不斷的落下,這裡遲早會冰封住
We"ll be buried alive!

717
01:08:22,450 --> 01:08:23,410
我們盡快走
We better get out!

718
01:08:26,720 --> 01:08:28,180
這兒是仙堡唯一的出口
This is the only way out.

719
01:08:28,390 --> 01:08:29,440
就是這兒
Here!

720
01:08:29,620 --> 01:08:31,590
這個洞我試過了,我不會游水會淹死我的
L"ve tried this hole before.I almost drowned.

721
01:08:31,760 --> 01:08:34,120
我不去,你們去吧,我不去
L"m not doing it again!You two go on ahead.L"m not going!

722
01:08:35,530 --> 01:08:37,690
我們拉他進去
Just drag him with us!

723
01:08:37,800 --> 01:08:39,850
不行,我不去,會淹死我的
No...No.L"ll drown!

724
01:08:43,630 --> 01:08:44,690
救命
Help!

725
01:09:10,090 --> 01:09:11,360
你幹什麼?
What"s the matter?

726
01:09:13,060 --> 01:09:15,530
我從來沒有離開過仙堡
L"ve never left the Fort in my life.

727
01:09:16,070 --> 01:09:19,520
現在我也不知道到哪兒去?
Where shall I go now?

728
01:09:19,940 --> 01:09:22,600
你到哪兒去?我不知道該怎麼說
I don"t know what to tell you.

729
01:09:23,110 --> 01:09:25,170
男兒志在四方
For men,the world is their domain.

730
01:09:25,480 --> 01:09:30,740
你一個女流之輩,不但不懂事整天就會哭
But you are a girl.And all you do is scream and cry.

731
01:09:30,980 --> 01:09:34,250
為了以後日子打算,不如到廟裡去做尼姑
Perhaps you should become a nun.

732
01:09:34,820 --> 01:09:37,080
生活雖然單調,你挺合適的
Life may be a little bland,but it"ll fit you fine.

733
01:09:37,620 --> 01:09:39,490
討厭,你少說兩句行不行?
What?Can"t you just shut up?

734
01:09:39,660 --> 01:09:42,630
我不會說話,想到什麼就說什麼
L"m not good with words,but that"s how I see it.

735
01:09:55,640 --> 01:09:57,110
十五,十六,十七
15,16,17...

736
01:10:00,940 --> 01:10:02,500
你過來幹什麼?
What do you want?

737
01:10:02,650 --> 01:10:04,910
一真,你記不記得,長眉叫我們去天刀峰
Yi-Chen,remember Long Brows asked us to go to Heaven"s Blade Peak

738
01:10:05,020 --> 01:10:06,570
找李亦奇和紫青雙劍
to find Li l-Chi and the Twin Swords.

739
01:10:07,480 --> 01:10:10,150
現在還剩半個月時間,如果再不去找
We have only half a month left.If we don"t hurry,

740
01:10:10,320 --> 01:10:13,590
元神出竅,天下正道人士就會大難臨頭
it will be doomsday for all when the Blood Demon egresses.

741
01:10:13,790 --> 01:10:15,450
仙堡裡的人我都救不了
We couldn"t even save those in the Fort.

742
01:10:15,630 --> 01:10:17,180
你還叫我想辦法救人家
How can we save anyone else?

743
01:10:18,100 --> 01:10:21,460
我本來是個西蜀兵,因為沒法子才當兵
I was originally a soldier from West Zu,but life for a soldier was unbearable.

744
01:10:21,700 --> 01:10:24,260
但求有一天有能人出現來搭救我們
I had hoped that someone would save us from self-destruction.

745
01:10:24,400 --> 01:10:27,270
後來碰到我的師父以為有救
Then I ran into our teachers and thought they were the ones to save us.

746
01:10:27,400 --> 01:10:32,570
沒想到正道人士不但肯團結,做事又遲慢
But the so-called righteous argued endlessly and refused to unite.

747
01:10:32,710 --> 01:10:33,970
現在紫青雙劍又沒找到
The Twin Swords have yet to be found,

748
01:10:34,210 --> 01:10:35,680
我跟師父已經四分五散了
and I have already lost my Teacher.

749
01:10:35,880 --> 01:10:37,740
他們只管自己門派的事
My teacher,like yours,cares only about his own clan.

750
01:10:37,880 --> 01:10:42,340
說是降妖服魔,守正辟邪普救天下
They talked about exorcising the demons and saving the world,

751
01:10:42,550 --> 01:10:43,920
其實是一盤散沙
but they"re just a bowl of loose sand.

752
01:10:44,090 --> 01:10:46,960
如果我們也像他們那樣,別說救他們
If we follow in their footsteps,

753
01:10:47,190 --> 01:10:49,750
就連我們這一代也不能自己救自己
we won"t even be able to save ourselves.

754
01:10:52,430 --> 01:10:54,990
說得對,師父師伯就是不肯團結
You"re right.The Blood Demon got his way

755
01:10:55,200 --> 01:10:56,670
所以才輸給邪魔
because my Teacher and Master Ting refused to work together.

756
01:10:57,330 --> 01:10:58,800
我們不能像他們那樣
We cannot be like them.

757
01:11:02,370 --> 01:11:04,030
那我們現在怎麼辦?
Where shall we go from here?

758
01:11:06,080 --> 01:11:08,640
我們三個人即刻起程,合力上天刀
We"ll go to Heaven"s Blade Peak immediately!

759
01:11:28,370 --> 01:11:29,130
天刀峰?
Heaven"s Blade Peak?

760
01:11:29,200 --> 01:11:30,170
地方這麼大
This place is huge!

761
01:11:30,300 --> 01:11:32,170
還有兩天,去哪兒找嗎?
We have two days left.How do we find Li l-Chi?

762
01:11:33,340 --> 01:11:34,200
是的
Yes.

763
01:11:34,710 --> 01:11:36,760
你們怎麼那麼笨,用嘴
You two are really dumb!Use your mouths!

764
01:11:37,040 --> 01:11:38,100
用嘴
Our mouths!

765
01:11:40,080 --> 01:11:42,550
李亦奇女俠
Lady Li l-Chi!

766
01:11:58,260 --> 01:11:59,230
快走
Run!

767
01:12:14,480 --> 01:12:16,640
豈有此理,用嘴找
Use our mouths!That was a stupid idea!

768
01:12:22,450 --> 01:12:23,610
你看那邊
Look over there!

769
01:12:25,790 --> 01:12:27,150
下面有個入口
There"s an entrance down there!

770
01:12:34,900 --> 01:12:37,770
江湖笑傲,唯我天刀
Heaven"s Blade is fearless and shuns the world!

771
01:12:42,670 --> 01:12:47,240
你們幾個來到這兒,究竟為了什麼事?
What are you all doing here?

772
01:12:48,550 --> 01:12:50,210
難道他就是李亦奇?
Is he Li l-Chi?

773
01:12:50,650 --> 01:12:52,620
你糊塗,李亦奇是女人
Don"t be foolish.Li is a woman.

774
01:12:55,250 --> 01:12:57,620
我問你們的問題還沒有答覆我
You have not answered my question.

775
01:12:59,260 --> 01:13:00,810
一點規矩都不懂
Where are your manners?

776
01:13:01,360 --> 01:13:05,320
你們知不知道剛才幾乎闖入了魔界
Did you know you almost stepped into Evil Territory just now?

777
01:13:08,670 --> 01:13:12,530
這兒就是天地之極神魔交界的地方
This is the border between Good and Evil.

778
01:13:12,840 --> 01:13:14,200
這是神魔交界?
Border?

779
01:13:14,440 --> 01:13:16,910
對了,你怎麼讓人鎖在這兒麼老伯?
By the way,who chained you here,Old Man?

780
01:13:17,240 --> 01:13:22,410
混帳,我不是老伯,我是天刀
Nonsense!L"m not Old Man!L"m Heaven"s Blade!

781
01:13:23,310 --> 01:13:25,280
天下間沒有能鎖得住我
No one in the world can chain down Heaven"s Blade!

782
01:13:33,320 --> 01:13:35,090
是我自己鎖住自己的
I chained myself here.

783
01:13:37,030 --> 01:13:38,790
你明知道這兒是魔界入口
Why did you chain yourself at

784
01:13:38,960 --> 01:13:40,120
為什麼還鎖著自己
the entrance to the Evil Territory?

785
01:13:42,930 --> 01:13:43,900
老伯
Old Man!

786
01:13:44,940 --> 01:13:46,600
你們走開,不用管我
Stay away!I can take care of myself!

787
01:13:57,010 --> 01:14:00,070
天地本為體,但神魔未盡一家
From the beginning of time,the Heavens and Earth were one.

788
01:14:02,750 --> 01:14:04,710
自從盤古開天,混沌以來
But the Gods and Devils were always at war.

789
01:14:05,180 --> 01:14:07,150
神魔鬥爭,已經相生不息
Never-ending wars.

790
01:14:07,550 --> 01:14:10,420
為了這樣,我天刀這兒費思百年
I have been here for over a century,

791
01:14:10,790 --> 01:14:12,250
為了三透個中道理
trying to understand the logic of this.

792
01:14:12,620 --> 01:14:15,180
結果反而被魔界的玄陰之氣所侵
But instead,I was invaded by the Evil Force.

793
01:14:15,530 --> 01:14:16,890
定力日漸消退
My strength is depleting fast.

794
01:14:17,260 --> 01:14:19,820
所以我沒辦法不鎖住自己
That is why I had to chain myself down.

795
01:14:20,900 --> 01:14:24,160
天地間有一個玄陰之氣流沛在宇宙之中
There is an evil force lurking in the universe.

796
01:14:24,530 --> 01:14:26,090
就因為有正氣所在
Because of an equally strong righteous force,

797
01:14:26,470 --> 01:14:28,440
所以才畏縮在地府之中
it stays in the Evil Territory.

798
01:14:28,910 --> 01:14:32,170
玄陰之氣就是天下自毀的魔性根源
This evil force is the basis of all self destruction.

799
01:14:32,540 --> 01:14:34,910
雖然它在魔界裡呼之欲出
Although it stays in the Evil Territory,

800
01:14:35,260 --> 01:14:38,300
但是它還支配著天下邪魔戰禍
it masterminds all evil wars and disasters on earth.

801
01:14:38,480 --> 01:14:42,040
玄陰之氣一朝未滅,天下永無太平
There will never be peace in the world as long as the Evil Force exists.

802
01:14:43,660 --> 01:14:48,120
可惜我天刀年數已長後繼無人
It is unfortunate that l"m old and

803
01:14:48,340 --> 01:14:49,700
只有留守這裡
can merely stand guard here.

804
01:14:50,270 --> 01:14:53,140
如果被邪魔闖入魔界
If any evil is able to get into the Evil Territory and unite with the Evil Force,

805
01:14:53,340 --> 01:14:55,710
它們的千年魔行,只需一朝了
the consequences will be too frightening to even ponder.

806
01:14:56,180 --> 01:14:58,640
難道天下間就沒人能破玄陰之氣嗎?
Is there no one who can destroy his Evil Force?

807
01:15:00,280 --> 01:15:02,940
現今天下正氣鋒芒已衰
The Righteous Force is weakening.

808
01:15:03,150 --> 01:15:06,920
後繼何人未必是紫青雙劍和李亦奇
Even Li l-Chi and the Twin Swords may not be able to succeed.

809
01:15:08,090 --> 01:15:10,960
李亦奇,她現在在哪兒?
Li l-Chi?Where is she?

810
01:15:11,990 --> 01:15:15,260
這兒是神魔交界有玄陰魔極
Since this is the border between the Good and Evil,

811
01:15:16,700 --> 01:15:19,460
當然也會有神城之府
the gods have their bases here too.

812
01:15:20,130 --> 01:15:22,900
她在你們右邊的天外天洞外洞
She is in the Cave Beyond to your right.

813
01:15:25,370 --> 01:15:26,840
我們終於找到她了
We"ve finally found her!

814
01:15:29,710 --> 01:15:31,080
可惜太遲了
It is too late!

815
01:15:31,550 --> 01:15:34,110
太遲了?她已經死了嗎,老伯?
Too late?Is she dead?

816
01:15:34,610 --> 01:15:36,580
混帳,你死了她沒死
Of course not.She will outlive all of you.

817
01:15:39,250 --> 01:15:42,620
我是說想不到我自己的功力退化得那麼多
What I meant was I did not realize my strength has deteriorated so much.

818
01:15:43,990 --> 01:15:46,360
有人進來這麼久,我現在才知道
It is only now that I detected a stranger"s presence.

819
01:15:52,100 --> 01:15:53,460
師父
Teacher!

820
01:15:57,140 --> 01:15:59,900
魔由心生,心生萬象
Evil comes from the heart.

821
01:16:00,510 --> 01:16:03,370
神為魔生,魔為神活
Gods come from devils.

822
01:16:03,940 --> 01:16:05,710
神魔本是一家
Good and evil are one

823
01:16:07,110 --> 01:16:10,080
天下間那有正邪之分
and the same.

824
01:16:10,350 --> 01:16:14,510
玄陰之氣,無上魔法
May the Evil Force live forever.

825
01:16:20,630 --> 01:16:21,590
他想入魔界
He wants to get into the Evil Territory!

826
01:16:34,410 --> 01:16:37,470
有我天刀在這兒你休想踏入魔界一步
You will have to get passed me,Heaven"s Blade,first.

827
01:17:11,780 --> 01:17:12,750
撞到我鼻子了
I hurt my nose!

828
01:17:25,760 --> 01:17:26,620
我們擋住他
Let"s stop him!

829
01:17:34,200 --> 01:17:35,260
七夕劍
Chi Hsi Sword?

830
01:17:36,040 --> 01:17:37,400
不錯,七夕劍
That"s right.

831
01:17:49,180 --> 01:17:53,050
七夕劍是正義之劍,我們似曾相識
Chi-Hsi Sword is a righteous sword,a sword I once knew.

832
01:17:53,390 --> 01:17:54,350
似曾相識?
The sword is the same,

833
01:17:54,550 --> 01:17:57,320
但是人事全非,除非你改邪歸正
but you have changed.Repent!

834
01:17:59,860 --> 01:18:01,120
不知不高地厚
You are too naive!

835
01:18:01,390 --> 01:18:03,360
就算天高地厚我也要扭轉乾坤
Naive or not,I must give it a try!

836
01:18:03,660 --> 01:18:05,820
天下已經夠亂,我不讓你踏入魔界
The world is already full of evil.L"ll not let you into the Evil Territory!

837
01:18:12,970 --> 01:18:14,840
螳臂擋車,不自量力
You obviously don"t know your limits!

838
01:18:32,730 --> 01:18:34,190
你還是這麼硬骨頭
You still insist?

839
01:18:39,130 --> 01:18:40,600
小卒子...
Soldier!!

840
01:18:52,710 --> 01:18:54,680
孺子可教不用怕,有我在這兒
Young man,you have a great potential.Don"t worry.L"m here.

841
01:18:59,720 --> 01:19:02,880
天刀,你的功力悉數耗盡
Heaven"s Blade,your strength is almost all gone.

842
01:19:03,790 --> 01:19:06,350
我勸你還是留著你的殘軀
You"d better save what"s left of your ragged body

843
01:19:06,930 --> 01:19:08,990
回鄉下貽養天年
to live a few more years.

844
01:19:09,900 --> 01:19:11,960
我的殘軀老體?
My ragged body?

845
01:19:12,130 --> 01:19:14,000
正邪相鬥成敗在於克敵意志
The battle between good and evil is a battle of wills.

846
01:19:14,430 --> 01:19:15,300
意志?
Wills?

847
01:19:15,570 --> 01:19:18,830
一個如日方中一個夕陽遲暮,沒有斗的
Your dying will is no match for my rising strength and power!

848
01:19:36,020 --> 01:19:37,080
你怎麼樣了?
Are you all right?

849
01:19:39,430 --> 01:19:41,790
這兒吸力很大,你們可別過來
The magnetic force is very strong over here.Stay away!

850
01:19:43,400 --> 01:19:46,260
你們快走,不走就走不了
Get out of here now before it"s too late!

851
01:19:48,000 --> 01:19:51,870
小卒了...你抓穩了別放手
Soldier...Hold on,don"t let go!

852
01:19:54,040 --> 01:19:57,100
小卒子...
Soldier...Soldier!

853
01:19:58,040 --> 01:20:02,610
小卒子...
Soldier!

854
01:20:05,750 --> 01:20:06,510
小心
Watch out!

855
01:20:17,000 --> 01:20:18,860
一真...
Yi-Chen!

856
01:20:22,870 --> 01:20:24,130
一真,你幹什麼?
Yi-Chen,what are you doing?

857
01:20:27,210 --> 01:20:30,670
我的膽子這麼小,我看也不能做掌門人了
L"ve always been a coward.L"m not fit to be the Chief.

858
01:20:35,450 --> 01:20:38,420
這串佛珠交給你,替我送回崑崙山吧
Here are the beads of the Chief.Please return them to Kun-Lun for me.

859
01:20:39,290 --> 01:20:40,340
那你呢?
Then what about you?

860
01:20:40,550 --> 01:20:43,420
小卒子現在在裡邊,還有機會去救他
Soldier is now inside.There"s still a chance to get him out.

861
01:20:43,520 --> 01:20:44,790
一真,我也跟你去
L"ll go with you!

862
01:20:46,330 --> 01:20:48,690
這怎麼行,如果我們兩個都不能出去
Don"t be silly.If we both can"t get out,

863
01:20:49,000 --> 01:20:50,160
誰去找紫青雙劍?
then who will find the Twin Swords?

864
01:20:50,560 --> 01:20:51,930
那麼我在這兒等你
L"ll wait for you here!

865
01:20:52,270 --> 01:20:55,830
你等我?
